{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c5650201-ab58-5c63-93c4-a9cf0fecfa09","excerpt":"Logo 取自 斜坡上的藝術節 粉絲團 在幾年前在 YouTube…","html":"<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/isenasenai/\"><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 720px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kacalisian 2019 logo\"\n        title=\"kacalisian 2019 logo\"\n        src=\"/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/51f8b/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 180w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/5aea8/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 360w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/8a6f4/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 720w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/72109/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 1080w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/182ac/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 1440w,\n/static/af5c940a97f55f6cc6095812d3696003/c5abd/kacalisian-2019-logo.jpg 1930w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></a></p>\n<p>Logo 取自<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/isenasenai/\">斜坡上的藝術節</a>粉絲團</p>\n<hr>\n<p>在幾年前在 YouTube 上亂晃發現了<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jb243ol_cCs\">嵐馨樂團</a>，一聽就被圈粉，原住民的幽默發揮的淋漓盡致，音樂又好聽。然後從而認識屏東在地的<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=59SKNU3-X7s\">小魯凱音樂傳創隊</a>，還有一直重複聽不膩的「<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RJMVsRBLytg\">阿佬啦</a>」樂團。</p>\n<p>前幾年就有注意到斜坡上系列的活動，但一直沒有行動力去參加… (明明那時候人就在屏東)，都是事後才看 YouTube 過過乾癮。這次在週四下午看到 FB 上有人分享，晚上就決定週五請假半天去修了很久發不太動的車直接殺過去參加。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"斜坡上的藝術節 2019","date":"November 04, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/kacalisian-2019/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/github-slang/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TL;DR? LGTM? 什麼意思？"}},"next":null}}